Задачи = текущие заказы + будущие заказы + внутренние

h1(#meetengs). Встречи
{code}

To reproduce this, do the following:

* Create two branches with different data
* Go to the branch view
* Select any branch with different data than the &#x27;main branch&#x27;
* From the single branch view, select &#x27;View Source&#x27;

Observe that the file contents of the main branch are shown and not the contents of that branch. To convince it to display properly, you&#x27;ll need to re-select the branch from the drop down.

